{"headings": [{"tag": "h1", "text": "Teodora Marchetti", "rect": {"x": 400, "y": 529.58, "width": 640, "height": 44, "bottom": 573.58, "right": 1040, "area": 28160}, "styles": {"fontSize": "35.2px", "fontWeight": "700", "fontFamily": "Georgia, \"Times New Roman\", Times, serif", "color": "rgb(184, 76, 30)", "backgroundColor": "rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)", "display": "block", "position": "static", "borderTopColor": "rgb(184, 76, 30)", "borderRightColor": "rgb(184, 76, 30)", "borderBottomColor": "rgb(184, 76, 30)", "borderLeftColor": "rgb(184, 76, 30)", "borderTopWidth": "0px", "borderRightWidth": "0px", "borderBottomWidth": "0px", "borderLeftWidth": "0px", "borderTopLeftRadius": "0px", "borderTopRightRadius": "0px", "borderBottomLeftRadius": "0px", "borderBottomRightRadius": "0px", "paddingTop": "0px", "paddingRight": "0px", "paddingBottom": "0px", "paddingLeft": "0px", "marginTop": "0px", "marginRight": "0px", "marginBottom": "24px", "marginLeft": "0px", "textAlign": "center", "boxShadow": "none", "backgroundImage": "none"}}, {"tag": "h2", "text": "Other Recipes in This Series", "rect": {"x": 400, "y": 1320.33, "width": 640, "height": 30, "bottom": 1350.33, "right": 1040, "area": 19200}, "styles": {"fontSize": "24px", "fontWeight": "700", "fontFamily": "Georgia, \"Times New Roman\", Times, serif", "color": "rgb(184, 76, 30)", "backgroundColor": "rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)", "display": "block", "position": "static", "borderTopColor": "rgb(184, 76, 30)", "borderRightColor": "rgb(184, 76, 30)", "borderBottomColor": "rgb(184, 76, 30)", "borderLeftColor": "rgb(184, 76, 30)", "borderTopWidth": "0px", "borderRightWidth": "0px", "borderBottomWidth": "0px", "borderLeftWidth": "0px", "borderTopLeftRadius": "0px", "borderTopRightRadius": "0px", "borderBottomLeftRadius": "0px", "borderBottomRightRadius": "0px", "paddingTop": "0px", "paddingRight": "0px", "paddingBottom": "0px", "paddingLeft": "0px", "marginTop": "0px", "marginRight": "0px", "marginBottom": "24px", "marginLeft": "0px", "textAlign": "start", "boxShadow": "none", "backgroundImage": "none"}}], "paragraphs": [{"text": "Cook, gardener, lifelong defender of a long, low oven.", "length": 54, "rect": {"x": 400, "y": 597.58, "width": 640, "height": 28.55, "bottom": 626.13, "right": 1040, "area": 18270}, "styles": {"fontSize": "16.8px", "fontWeight": "400", "fontFamily": "system-ui, -apple-system, \"system-ui\", \"Segoe UI\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif", "color": "rgb(26, 18, 16)", "backgroundColor": "rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)", "display": "block", "position": "static", "borderTopColor": "rgb(26, 18, 16)", "borderRightColor": "rgb(26, 18, 16)", "borderBottomColor": "rgb(26, 18, 16)", "borderLeftColor": "rgb(26, 18, 16)", "borderTopWidth": "0px", "borderRightWidth": "0px", "borderBottomWidth": "0px", "borderLeftWidth": "0px", "borderTopLeftRadius": "0px", "borderTopRightRadius": "0px", "borderBottomLeftRadius": "0px", "borderBottomRightRadius": "0px", "paddingTop": "0px", "paddingRight": "0px", "paddingBottom": "0px", "paddingLeft": "0px", "marginTop": "0px", "marginRight": "0px", "marginBottom": "24px", "marginLeft": "0px", "textAlign": "center", "boxShadow": "none", "backgroundImage": "none"}}, {"text": "Teodora grew up in a third-floor flat above a fishmonger in Genoa, where the windows opened onto the smell of salt and basil and the kitchen never quite stopped working. Her grandmother kept a copper pot on the back burner from morning into evening, and the rule of the house was simple: nothing was rushed, nothing was wasted, and a beans-and-greens supper could carry a family through any kind of week.", "length": 404, "rect": {"x": 400, "y": 763.13, "width": 640, "height": 173.34, "bottom": 936.47, "right": 1040, "area": 110940}, "styles": {"fontSize": "17px", "fontWeight": "400", "fontFamily": "system-ui, -apple-system, \"system-ui\", \"Segoe UI\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif", "color": "rgb(26, 18, 16)", "backgroundColor": "rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)", "display": "block", "position": "static", "borderTopColor": "rgb(26, 18, 16)", "borderRightColor": "rgb(26, 18, 16)", "borderBottomColor": "rgb(26, 18, 16)", "borderLeftColor": "rgb(26, 18, 16)", "borderTopWidth": "0px", "borderRightWidth": "0px", "borderBottomWidth": "0px", "borderLeftWidth": "0px", "borderTopLeftRadius": "0px", "borderTopRightRadius": "0px", "borderBottomLeftRadius": "0px", "borderBottomRightRadius": "0px", "paddingTop": "0px", "paddingRight": "0px", "paddingBottom": "0px", "paddingLeft": "0px", "marginTop": "0px", "marginRight": "0px", "marginBottom": "24px", "marginLeft": "0px", "textAlign": "start", "boxShadow": "none", "backgroundImage": "none"}}, {"text": "She moved to Edinburgh in her late twenties, trading the Ligurian coast for a stone tenement and a small back garden that now grows more rosemary than it has any right to. Her cooking sits somewhere between those two places \u00e2\u20ac\u201d Italian patience translated through a Scottish pantry. She writes about food the way she cooks it: slowly, plainly, and with a deep suspicion of any recipe that promises to be quick.", "length": 410, "rect": {"x": 400, "y": 960.47, "width": 640, "height": 144.45, "bottom": 1104.92, "right": 1040, "area": 92450}, "styles": {"fontSize": "17px", "fontWeight": "400", "fontFamily": "system-ui, -apple-system, \"system-ui\", \"Segoe UI\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif", "color": "rgb(26, 18, 16)", "backgroundColor": "rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)", "display": "block", "position": "static", "borderTopColor": "rgb(26, 18, 16)", "borderRightColor": "rgb(26, 18, 16)", "borderBottomColor": "rgb(26, 18, 16)", "borderLeftColor": "rgb(26, 18, 16)", "borderTopWidth": "0px", "borderRightWidth": "0px", "borderBottomWidth": "0px", "borderLeftWidth": "0px", "borderTopLeftRadius": "0px", "borderTopRightRadius": "0px", "borderBottomLeftRadius": "0px", "borderBottomRightRadius": "0px", "paddingTop": "0px", "paddingRight": "0px", "paddingBottom": "0px", "paddingLeft": "0px", "marginTop": "0px", "marginRight": "0px", "marginBottom": "24px", "marginLeft": "0px", "textAlign": "start", "boxShadow": "none", "backgroundImage": "none"}}, {"text": "A good braise forgives almost everything except impatience.", "length": 59, "rect": {"x": 400, "y": 1144.92, "width": 640, "height": 135.41, "bottom": 1280.33, "right": 1040, "area": 86660}, "styles": {"fontSize": "24.8px", "fontWeight": "400", "fontFamily": "Georgia, \"Times New Roman\", Times, serif", "color": "rgb(26, 18, 16)", "backgroundColor": "rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)", "display": "block", "position": "static", "borderTopColor": "rgb(212, 184, 154)", "borderRightColor": "rgb(26, 18, 16)", "borderBottomColor": "rgb(212, 184, 154)", "borderLeftColor": "rgb(26, 18, 16)", "borderTopWidth": "1px", "borderRightWidth": "0px", "borderBottomWidth": "1px", "borderLeftWidth": "0px", "borderTopLeftRadius": "0px", "borderTopRightRadius": "0px", "borderBottomLeftRadius": "0px", "borderBottomRightRadius": "0px", "paddingTop": "32px", "paddingRight": "16px", "paddingBottom": "32px", "paddingLeft": "16px", "marginTop": "40px", "marginRight": "0px", "marginBottom": "40px", "marginLeft": "0px", "textAlign": "center", "boxShadow": "none", "backgroundImage": "none"}}, {"text": "For questions about this recipe, or to share a photograph of your own pot at the three-hour mark, write to teodora@copperkettlesuppers.test.", "length": 140, "rect": {"x": 400, "y": 1766.17, "width": 640, "height": 47.59, "bottom": 1813.77, "right": 1040, "area": 30460}, "styles": {"fontSize": "14px", "fontWeight": "400", "fontFamily": "system-ui, -apple-system, \"system-ui\", \"Segoe UI\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif", "color": "rgb(26, 18, 16)", "backgroundColor": "rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)", "display": "block", "position": "static", "borderTopColor": "rgb(26, 18, 16)", "borderRightColor": "rgb(26, 18, 16)", "borderBottomColor": "rgb(26, 18, 16)", "borderLeftColor": "rgb(26, 18, 16)", "borderTopWidth": "0px", "borderRightWidth": "0px", "borderBottomWidth": "0px", "borderLeftWidth": "0px", "borderTopLeftRadius": "0px", "borderTopR